{
  "stem": "23498.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Otwalska. ?] That was the place where the-- many people were going for holidays, you know, fresh air, not far from Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was a-- a little sort of train going and, you know, very noisy, and everyone knew that line.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- but [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Radocz ?] was especially Polish place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And she said, I've got a-- the family, they've got one daughter.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And maybe-- it's a-- you know, they are very poor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They used to be-- he used to be-- he used to work in a office.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they're class people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And maybe-- I don't promise anything.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they made a meeting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the woman said, I have to agree, because I'm already keeping a Jewish boy.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "The boy was seven or something like that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they took him, because they were poor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the parents were from another town.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The-- the mother was-- the father was a solicitor and mother was also professional-- I can't recall.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They both-- the father, when he came last time-- what was Mrs.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Poniewierski who was hiding us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She was telling me afterwards, she could see that he's a goner.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was-- The father-- that the father was?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He wasn't-- he didn't look Jewish, but he was a goner.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He resigned.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was-- he didn't have the power to fight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He lost it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she knew it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was the mother who was coming also.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the mother apparently wanted to go to Germany, because she was looking Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they caught her and killed her on the spot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She was already on the [?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] ?] side.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was the boy left, to whom they were very, very attached.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they wanted to keep the-- the child.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
